      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺が気にするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I do mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.982176844278971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 10.748730127016703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと結べるようになったよね\nネクタイ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aw‚ you’re able to tie it properly now.\nYour necktie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.202131466698225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 14.582063460350033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "前は、いつも変な結び方になって\n三枝さんに怒られてたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You used to always tie it really weird\nand Mr. Saegusa would yell at you‚ remember?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.415396793683364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did he?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.78206346035003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 21.27424035072326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "私がいつも直してあげてたんだよ\nもうっ！　とか言いながら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ and I always fixed your tie for you.\nAnd you’d grumble‚ “Stop it.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.27424035072326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 26.24090701738993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだ。そのせいで仲を疑われたこともあったな）\n（それでまた三枝さんに怒られたんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(That’s right. Because of that‚ some people misinterpreted our relationship.)\n(Which made Mr. Saegusa angry again.)",
        "id": ""
