      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、どこに行くの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ where are you going?",
        "id": ""
