      "text": "知り合い多いんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sure have a lot of acquaintances here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_08-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "長く入院していましたからね\nみんながいてくれたから、落ち込まずにいられたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I was hospitalized here for a long time.\nAnd everyone here helped keep me from getting too depressed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
