      "text": "（彼女が背負ってきた苦労は大きい。それだけ）\n（今こうやって歌える喜びも大きいんだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The burden of pain she’s been carrying is huge. That explains)\n(why she sings with such a huge amount of joy today.)",
